      <title>印度农民因雨水充沛而增加稻米和豆类的种植</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/indian-farmers-boost-planting-of-rice-and-pulses-on-good-rain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于本季节迄今为止的季风降雨量高于平均水平，印度的水稻和豆类作物的播种面积有所增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/indian-farmers-boost-planting-of-rice-and-pulses-on-good-rain</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 08:58:39 GMT</pubDate>
